data.description: Welcome to your Carlsbad dream home! Charming townhouse in the highly desirable community of Meadowridge! 3 bed 2.5 bath with an attached 1 car garage, extra parking in the driveway, an assigned parking spot, and private storage space! Featuring a beautiful open-concept layout, this rarely available attached home is the paradigm of contemporary Southern California living. It offers both privacy and a comfortable lifestyle.  Once inside, a soothing neutral palette and vast windows work to create a captivating interior with a high-end feel. Bathed in natural light & accented with an elegant fireplace, the spacious living room offers a perfect balance for casual lounging or hosting gatherings alike, while sliding glass doors work to unite the interior to the deck. Delightful eat-in kitchen equipped with breakfast bar seating, a sizable pantry, recessed lighting & an adjacent formal dining room with picturesque windows, as well as a conveniently located main-level half bathroom. Downstairs features an oversized primary suite with an ensuite bathroom and sliding glass doors, two spacious secondary bedrooms, and an additional full bathroom. Some desirable Meadowridge amenities include a sparkling pool and spa, and tennis courts. The new roof will be installed in Dec. 2023 by the HOA. Conveniently located in the top-rated San Marcos School District, this home is just minutes away from shopping, dining, parks, golf amenities, hiking trails, Carlsbad beaches, I-5, Highway 78, & more. Multiple options are available to help you get into this home. Seller motivated and open to a buyer closing cost credit or rate buy down. Seller's loan could be assumable with lender approval.
